snippet.title: NKANDLA The Truth - What Scares Jacob Zuma.

localized.description:
What is Jacob Zuma scared of? Will Julius Malema of the Economic Freedom Fighters (EFF) rule another Planet?  Is ISON or Nibiru going to struck Earth?  Nelson Mandela is dead. Is this Fact or Fiction? Watch the video, and you decide.
Relax people - This is satire!
With respect to President Zuma and the ANC, Former President the late Mr. Mandela and his family as well as Mr Malema.
